(86, 'Ekiti Children Funfair', 'EVT_16069398964957', '<p>VISIT FATHER CHRISTMAS SECRET CHAMBERS IN ADO EKITI ON DECEMBER 11</p><p>Come and meet Father Christmas at his secret chambers on Friday, 11 December 2020 from 2 pm-6 pm, at the playground, Kiibati Hotels, and Resort, Ado Ekiti.</p><p>Children will get 4 hour-long Christmas experience with music, games, cartoons, a castle playground, and of course, gifts from the real Father Christmas.</p><p>All children must be accompanied by an adult at all times. Ekiti Children\'s funfair can be enjoyed by all ages and is most suitable for children ages 3-12.</p><p>The momentous experience begins Friday, 11 December 2020 by 2 pm and ends at 6 pm.</p><p>Tickets are on sale now for N1,000 per child. To get tickets, please contact @oneekiti or @debiwumi (oneekitiofficial@gmail.com and +2349037228640).</p>', '2020-12-11', '2020-12-11', 'uploads/16069398961838402WhatsApp_Image_2020_12_02_at_9.05.39_PM.jpeg', '1576161374_5710325', '08:11:36', '2020-12-02', 'thumb/16069398968684034WhatsApp_Image_2020_12_02_at_9.05.39_PM.jpeg', 0, '2pm - 6pm', 'Playground Kiibati Hotels, and Resort, Ado Ekiti.', 'One Ekiti', '<p>Details Later</p>', NULL, NULL, 'show', '5.237108699999999', '7.6124263', 'Nigeria [NG]', 'Ekiti', 'Ado', 30798, 2660, 160, 1, '2020-12-11', NULL, 969, NULL, '1', 'ekitichildrenfunfair', NULL, '231r23cfre2', 3088, 'Ekiti,Children,Funfair,OneEkiti', 'paid', 'single', '1000', '1', NULL, 'a:6:{s:28:\"Q2hpbGQncyBEYXRlIE9mIEJpcnRo\";a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:28:\"Q2hpbGQncyBEYXRlIE9mIEJpcnRo\";s:8:\"question\";s:21:\"Child\'s Date Of Birth\";s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"date\";s:7:\"options\";b:0;s:8:\"required\";b:1;}s:32:\"Q2hpbGQncyBMb2NhbCBHb3Zlcm5tZW50\";a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:32:\"Q2hpbGQncyBMb2NhbCBHb3Zlcm5tZW50\";s:8:\"question\";s:24:\"Child\'s Local Government\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"single\";s:7:\"options\";b:0;s:8:\"required\";b:1;}s:16:\"SG9tZSBBZGRyZXNz\";a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:16:\"SG9tZSBBZGRyZXNz\";s:8:\"question\";s:12:\"Home Address\";s:4:\