(232, 'SAFE SUMMIT 3.0 ', 'EVT_16629844753576', '<p>This year\'s summit is focused on the sub-Sahara African agricultural vegetable value chain ecosystem. The event is designed to ignite discussions around value addition in the vegetable value chain and it\'s primary potentials to promote, foreign exchange earnings, international trade and Agro-tourism.<br><br>The theme for SAFE SUMMIT 3.0 is: \"Value Addition in Vegetable Value Chains: The sub-Sahara African Prospect.\"<br><br>Location is Ado Ekiti, the capital of Ekiti State, Nigeria.<br>This year will play host to policy makers, thought leaders in the vegetable value and supply chains, and insightful panel sessions.<br><br>For updates and inquiries, kindly stay tune to any of our social media platforms</p>', '2022-12-01', '2022-12-01', 'uploads/1662984475341697unnamed__35_.jpg', '1537374982obusn6a8u39t94101n5ol', '12:07:55', '2022-09-12', 'uploads/1662984475341697unnamed__35_.jpg', 0, '10am - 3PM', 'Arowolo Ball Room,Arowolo Gadren, Beside Ayoba FM,  Fajuyi', 'RAISE A FARMER INAITITIVE', '<p>Raise A Farmer Initiative Identifies,trains and mentors youth in vegetable farming and incorporate them into the business of #agriculture</p>', NULL, NULL, 'hide', '', '', 'Nigeria [NG]', 'Ekiti', 'Ado', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', 'Test', NULL, '231rcfre2', 54, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '--Select Virtual Platform--', 'a:1:{s:12:\"Q291bnRyeSA=\";a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:12:\"Q291bnRyeSA=\";s:8:\"question\";s:8:\"Country \";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"single\";s:7:\"options\";b:0;s:8:\"required\";b:1;}}', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Event', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#a5db01', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(233, 'Youth Coding Bootcamp', 'EVT_16631921206758', '<p>This youth Code Academy is to create awareness for young people in the City of Ibadan and environs to the amazing opprtunities available for them in the tech Industry and to help them create future careers and be able to use their virtual time more profitably. This code academy will start online with physical Classes where they can meet their teachers one on one.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-10-08', '2022-10-22', 'uploads/1663192119794527IMG_20220914_WA0018.jpg', '1663192160_1324302', '09:48:40', '2022-09-14', 'uploads/1663192119794527IMG_20220914_WA0018.jpg', 0, '6pm - 7pm', 'Virrual', 'Roserock Academy with Mom', '<p>Roserock Academy makes education possible virtually and Online. All our Classes are done virtually with momentum physical classes.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, 'hide', '', '', 'Nigeria [NG]', 'Oyo', 'Ibadan', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'YouthCodingBootcamp', NULL, '231rcfr32', NULL, '#tech, #youth #careers #remotework #earnings', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Whatsapp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Training', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
