(253, 'no to body shaming', 'EVT_16717771446752', '<p><i>Just Maki</i>ng payment</p>', '2022-12-23', '2026-12-23', 'uploads/1671777143465166333.jpg', '16717766988a9i1od5l5rboc50nty983ote', '06:32:24', '2022-12-23', 'uploads/1671777143465166333.jpg', 0, '07:00am-09:00pm', NULL, 'notobodyshaming', '<p>The organization.<br>Starting a movement that creates awareness on what body shaming is and how it is affecting our mental health stemmed out of the founderâ€™s personal experiences. The founder, who is a professional model and Ex beauty queen with crowns and awards to her name, was shamed as a model. The obvious discrimination and discrepancy between peoples bodies and what a model should look like with huge disregard to who is healthy is daunting. This was owing to the fact that she is considered a plus size and didnâ€™t fit into the societyâ€™s â€œidealâ€ model figure. Refusing to be defined by the industryâ€™s standard and understanding the fact that Body shaming in all it hidden forms is deeply ingrained in most aspects of our lives, the founder took on measures to promote body positivity in a bird to curb shaming in all its forms.</p>', NULL, NULL, 'hide', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, '2026-12-23', NULL, 499, NULL, '1', 'notobodyshaming', NULL, 'BGRT64GF5dw', 21, '', 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL, '--Select Virtual Platform--', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'NGN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'a:2:{s:2:\"dc\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"link\";s:37:\"https://notobodyshaming1.wixsite.com/\";}', 'Event', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Register', '<p>Welcome</p>', NULL, NULL),
