(270, 'Ekiti Campus Easter/ Ramadan Hangout', 'EVT_16794985901461', '<p>Join us for an unforgettable experience at the <strong>Ekiti Campus Easter/Ramadan Hangout</strong>, brought to you by <strong>Alexander Entertainment/Ibadan Hangouts Team</strong>. This open-air event promises to be a fun-filled gathering where attendees can socialize, relax, and enjoy themselves in a safe environment.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The event will be hosted by the talented <strong>MC Alexander</strong> and will feature top entertainers who will perform and be recognized for their outstanding contributions. In addition, we will be presenting <strong>the third season of the Fasa Awards</strong>, showcasing the best in entertainment.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>There will be plenty of side attractions to keep you engaged, including face painting, mask-up, linkups, outdoor games, platoon games, and more. Whether you\'re looking for a romantic evening or an opportunity to network with like-minded people, our Love/Fasting Fiesta has something for everyone.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The event will take place on <strong>April 8, 2023</strong>, at the <strong>D Bar Arena, located along Motif Funland, Vicolas Estate, Iworoko.&nbsp;</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><ol><li>Ticket prices are reasonable:</li><li>Regular tickets at #500.</li><li>VIP tickets at #2000.</li><li>Table reservations for three (3) are available for #10,000.</li><li>Exclusive access for five (5) can be secured for #20,000.</li></ol><p>The event starts with a red carpet ceremony at <strong>2 pm</strong>, and you can purchase tickets by visiting our bio @Fasa_Awards_Eksu or Ib_City_hangouts or via WhatsApp at <strong>08139065694</strong>.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Don\'t miss out on this unique opportunity to be part of the Ekiti Campus Easter/Ramadan Hangout, a replica of the highly successful Ibadan Hangouts events.</p>', '2023-04-08', '2023-04-08', '2024/03/29/uploads/171170300521284images__6_.jpg', '1671808628e9ala802t0r99cxniarle623ed', '03:23:10', '2023-03-22', '2024/03/29/uploads/171170300521284images__6_.jpg', 0, '2pm', 'D bar Arena, Iworoko along Motif funland, Vicolas Estate.', 'MC Alexander', '<p>Organized by <strong>MC Alexander,</strong> the Ekiti Campus Easter/Ramadan Hangout promises to be an unforgettable experience brought to you by Alexander Entertainment and the Ibadan Hangouts Team. This open-air event is designed to create a fun-filled gathering where attendees can socialize, relax, and enjoy themselves in a safe environment.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>MC Alexander will be hosting the event, and top entertainers will perform and be recognized for their outstanding contributions. Additionally, the third season of the Fasa Awards will be presented, showcasing the best in entertainment.</p>', NULL, NULL, 'show', '', '', 'Nigeria [NG]', 'Ekiti', 'Ado', 30798, 2660, 160, 1, '2023-04-08', NULL, 1000000, NULL, '1', 'Ekiti-Campus_Hangout', NULL, '231r23cfre2', 1504, NULL, 'paid', 'categorized', '500', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'NGN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Event', NULL, NULL, '+2348139065694 ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#f38000', 'Get Ticket', '<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, NULL),
