(273, 'EKITI MIDDLE ECONOMY CONFERENCE 1.0', 'EVT_16806928253682', '<p>The Middle Economy Summit seeks to reduce graduate unemployment and increase the availability of jobs in the labour market by training and helping to create employers of labour. The conference also seeks to train young entrepreneurs how to kick-start their businesses with zero capital and grow a sustainable business starting as a bridge in their choosing industry.&nbsp;</p><p>To train entrepreneurs on how to start from the zero level, we rely on the success stories of successful entrepreneurs in different industries who built profitable and sustainable businesses starting from the zero level. We engage the best whose beginning is similar to our audience to give general and specialized training, and share knowledge and informed perspective on the process of building something big and sustainable out of little or nothing.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>In a simpler form, we bring top experts in different fields of enterprise to give general training on entrepreneurship, monitor and mentor trainees in their chosen entrepreneurship field, empower them by providing advice on how to mobilize capital and access funding and educate them on how to convert their social tractions and relationships to venture/seed capitals.&nbsp;</p>', '2023-06-10', '2023-06-10', 'uploads/16848764874311595WhatsApp_Image_2023_05_23_at_18.58.44.jpg', '16841414692e01l7ll3w89reo7taaa6ic2', '11:07:05', '2023-04-05', 'uploads/16848764874311595WhatsApp_Image_2023_05_23_at_18.58.44.jpg', 0, '11AM', 'Ali Arowolo Ball Room at Arowolo Gardens Fajuyi Ado Ekiti', 'Olawale Kadri', '<p>Olawale Kadri is the Project Lead of The Possible Group and the organizer of The Middle Economy Summit. The main objective of the summit is to reduce graduate unemployment and increase job availability in the labor market by training and helping to create employers of labor. The summit also seeks to train young entrepreneurs on how to kick-start their businesses with zero capital and grow a sustainable business starting as a bridge in their chosen industry.&nbsp;<br><br>Olawale Kadri is committed to reducing graduate unemployment and increasing job availability in the labor market by empowering young entrepreneurs with the knowledge, skills, and tools they need to start and grow sustainable businesses.</p>', NULL, NULL, 'hide', '', '', 'Nigeria [NG]', 'Ekiti', 'Ado', 30798, 2660, 160, 1, '2023-06-10', NULL, 43, NULL, '1', 'EMEC', NULL, '231rcfre2', 3315, '', 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'a:1:{s:8:\"R2VuZGVy\";a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:8:\"R2VuZGVy\";s:8:\"question\";s:6:\"Gender\";s:4:\"type\";s:7:\"options\";s:7:\"options\";a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"Male\";i:1;s:6:\"Female\";}s:8:\"required\";b:1;}}', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'a:5:{s:28:\"UmV2IFR1bmRlIEFmZSAgL2FsbA==\";a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:28:\"UmV2IFR1bmRlIEFmZSAgL2FsbA==\";s:4:\"name\";s:15:\"Rev Tunde Afe  \";s:11:\"designation\";s:29:\"Pastor, Farmer and Consultant\";s:5:\"about\";s:48:\"Rev Tunde Afe is a Pastor, Farmer and Consultant\";s:5:\"image\";s:37:\"uploads/168373655170534base_image.png\";}s:36:\"VG9iaSBBYnJhaGFtIEFrb21vbGFmZS9hbGw=\";a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:36:\"VG9iaSBBYnJhaGFtIEFrb21vbGFmZS9hbGw=\";s:4:\"name\";s:22:\"Tobi Abraham Akomolafe\";s:11:\"designation\";s:34:\"Tech Lead, Abba Infotech Resources\";s:5:\"about\";s:65:\"Tobi Abraham Akomolafe is the Tech Lead, Abba Infotech Resources.\";s:5:\"image\";s:37:\"uploads/168380799790291base_image.png\";}s:32:\"QmFyciBUb3lvc2kgQXllbGVzby9hbGw=\";a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:32:\"QmFyciBUb3lvc2kgQXllbGVzby9hbGw=\";s:4:\"name\";s:19:\"Barr Toyosi Ayeleso\";s:11:\"designation\";s:36:\"Principal Partner, Csi International\";s:5:\"about\";s:65:\"Barr Toyosi Ayeleso is the Principal Partner of Csi International\";s:5:\"image\";s:37:\"uploads/168380812532172base_image.png\";}s:24:\"VG9wZSBCYW5kZWxlL2FsbA==\";a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:24:\"VG9wZSBCYW5kZWxlL2FsbA==\";s:4:\"name\";s:12:\"Tope Bandele\";s:11:\"designation\";s:19:\"Life/Business Coach\"