(286, 'Sunshine mountain safari  1.0', 'EVT_16872197028585', '<p>Ondo mountain safari is an annual program that seeks to bring together all mountain lovers from all around the world to explore the beauty of ONDO state intriguing landscape, this will also serve as an avenue to promote ondo state as the most preferred destination to witness the&nbsp; most enchanting hills and mountains adventure in&nbsp; Nigeria.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p>Our aim is to showcase and get people familiar with all the beautiful mountain in Ondo state, Ondo state mountain safari will subsequently change venue of the program per time until weâ€™ve showcased and promote all the beautiful landscapes in our dear state.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p>For 2023 we will be using the new Lacampagne Tropicana hills, cave and forest resort in in Ita nla Ondo town.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p>The hills has a very beautiful landscape and its also been found by our tourism ambassador in Ondo state. Otunba wanle Akinboboye who has earned Global recognition by building the most distinctive destination in Africa, providing visitors with a blend of natural beauty, cultural immersion, and sustainable tourism practices.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p>Ondo mountain safari will be welcoming tourist from all over World, to witness this beautiful program.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p>This program will also be an avenue for art vendors to exhibit their work in the faces of tourist from all over the world.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p>This Event will be divided into to segments, (Day &amp; Night)</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p>Day activities includes,</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p>Hiking</p><p>Art exhibition</p><p>Performances (standup comedy, Dance , acrobatic)</p><p>Games (basket ball, Aim the basket, football)</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p>Night activities includes ,</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p>Performance</p><p>Born fire</p><p>Pool party</p><p>Karaoke</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Naija safari x sunshine tourism</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p>Ondo Mountain Safar