(306, 'ArtMesh: Open Mic + MeetUp for Creatives', 'EVT_16932382951885', '<p><i><strong>ARTMESH is held on the First Friday of the month at the American Corner, Ikeja (42, Local Airport Road, Ikeja, Lagos).</strong></i></p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p>We want to build a fun and open environment for writers, storytellers, spoken word artists, poets, and everyone else involved in the creative space.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p>Whether you are a performer, a lover of art/literature, or a friend to one, we\'d love you to join us!</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p>If you are interested in performing, kindly contact the host upon arrival or send a message across via <strong>WhatsApp (+2348117230203)</strong></p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p>We look forward to hosting new and experieced writers and performers.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>AGENDA:</strong></p><ol><li>Introduction</li><li>First games</li><li>Open Mic</li><li>See a Short film, quick discuss</li><li>Creative Discussion</li><li>Open Mic II</li><li>Introduce the late arrivals</li><li>Photo-bombay</li><li>Meet\'N\'Greet [at the rooftop]</li></ol><p><br><br>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>VENUE</strong></p><p><i>American Corner, Ikeja</i> has been home for ARTMESH and continues to house numerous creatives monthtly.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Time: 2.00pm - 5.00pm [MeetUp Commences after the program]</strong></p><p>Contact our program team <strong>+2348117230203</strong></p>', '2023-10-06', '2023-10-06', '2024/03/29/uploads/17117011046905336190c58b8f8fdf17523d8fb2ad94be023fa3cb8b0da8b1436f93098d326be0978_rimg_w1200_h600_gmir.webp', '1608781742ar872utth2l2ta8iec335r', '03:58:15', '2023-08-28', '2024/03/29/uploads/17117011046905336190c58b8f8fdf17523d8fb2ad94be023fa3cb8b0da8b1436f93098d326be0978_rimg_w1200_h600_gmir.webp', 0, '2:00pm - 5:00pm', 'American Corner Ikeja 42, Local Airport Road, Concord Bus/stop, Ikeja, Lagos', 'ArtHut', '<p>ArtHut is a creative community dedicated towards #TellingOurOwnStories</