(336, 'Party with Pivotal - Rave Therapy Edition', 'EVT_17116363436897', '<p>Set against the vibrant backdrop of Ibadan\'s lively cultural scene, \"Party with Pivotal\" is poised to redefine the nightlife experience with its Rave Therapy Edition. On the evening of April 20th, the Recreation Club Pool Arena will transform into a pulsating hub of music and movement, inviting you to lose yourself in the rhythm and find solace in the beat.</p><p>As the sun sets, the red carpet will roll out, heralding the commencement of an electrifying journey at 6:30 PM, where fashion meets fervor. As the clock strikes 8:00 PM, the heart of the event will beat in sync with the sounds of the latest hits and the energy of the crowd, promising an unforgettable night where connections are forged in the glow of neon lights and the spirit of revelry.</p><p>In a city that thrums with the hearts of its people, \"Party with Pivotal\" is not just an event; it\'s a collective escape into a world where the music cures, the atmosphere intoxicates, and the night promises the magic of discovery. Join the movement; become part of the story that will be told and retold, long after the last note fades into the dawn.</p>', '2024-04-20', '2024-04-20', '2024/03/28/uploads/17116363435211669Artboard_1.jpg', 'j90819542aBn72i', '02:32:23', '2024-03-28', '2024/03/28/uploads/17116363435211669Artboard_1.jpg', 0, '18:00', 'Recreation Club Pool Arena,Sabo, Ibadan', 'Pivotal', '<p>pwp</p>', NULL, NULL, 'show', '', '', 'Nigeria [NG]', 'Oyo', 'Ibadan', 31064, 2677, 160, 1, '2024-04-20', NULL, 4999, NULL, '1', 'pwp7', NULL, '231r23cfre2', 1666, 'pwp,partywithpivotal,partywithpivotal7,pwp7', 'paid', 'categorized', '4000', '1', NULL, NULL, '6145037788_1711643663', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'NGN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Event', NULL, NULL, '+2348054991839', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#015f67', 'Get Ticket', '<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, NULL);
