(337, 'Osun Osogbo Opening Ceremony  ', 'EVT_17133559507395', '<p>Join us for the grand opening ceremony of the Osun Osogbo Festival, a celebration deeply rooted in Yoruba culture and tradition. &nbsp;Esteemed festival organizers and local dignitaries will extend their warmest greetings, welcoming guests from near and far to partake in this vibrant cultural extravaganza.</p>', '2024-08-14', '2024-08-14', '2024/04/17/uploads/17133562294557498pexels_thibault_trillet_167491__1__11zon__1_.jpg', '1684241596li0cp67l8i2ph8e4tr98ai5', '12:12:30', '2024-04-17', '2024/04/17/uploads/17133562294557498pexels_thibault_trillet_167491__1__11zon__1_.jpg', 0, '06- 09pm', 'Osogbo Stadium, Osogbo, Osun State. ', 'Osun Osogbo Team ', '<p>The organizers of the Osun Osogbo Festival are esteemed custodians of Yoruba culture and tradition, dedicated to preserving and celebrating its rich heritage. With deep reverence for the festival\'s significance, they meticulously plan every detail, ensuring a memorable experience for all attendees. Comprised of local dignitaries and cultural enthusiasts, they extend their warmest greetings to guests from near and far, inviting them to immerse themselves in the vibrant cultural buzz of the festival.</p>', NULL, NULL, 'show', '', '', 'Nigeria [NG]', 'Osun', 'Oshogbo', 31058, 2676, 160, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'osun_osogbo_opening_ceremony', NULL, '231r231002345433rrrr23', 287, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Event', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
