(392, 'TSLC TECH FEST', 'EVT_17251290134561', '<p>This tech fest is designed to explore the intersection of data security and privacy rights in an increasingly digital world. The event will bring together industry leaders, tech enthusiasts, policy makers, and students to discuss the latest advancements, challenges, and strategies in safeguarding personal and organizational data. It is also aimed at students interested in the rapidly evolving fields of data security and privacy. This event will provide an engaging platform for students to learn about the importance of protecting data, explore emerging technologies, and understand their roles in shaping the future of data security. Through interactive sessions, workshops, and discussions, attendees will gain valuable insights into how data protection impacts their lives and future careers. This Tech Fest will also provide a platform for sharing innovative solutions and best practices for maintaining data integrity and privacy.</p>', '2024-11-16', '2024-11-16', '2024/08/31/uploads/172512901267520521000945538_02.jpeg', '1725003018_1856165', '06:30:13', '2024-08-31', '2024/08/31/uploads/172512901267520521000945538_02.jpeg', 0, '10:00', 'Ekiti State University, Iworoko', 'Tech Savvy Law Club', '<p>Tech Savvy Law Club (TSLC), Ekiti State University (EKSU), is an association formed under the Tech Savvy Lawyers\' Network (TSLN). As the parent body, TSLN is a professional organization established and dedicated to bridging the knowledge gap in global technology law practice in the Nigerian legal ecosystem.</p>', NULL, NULL, 'show', NULL, NULL, 'Nigeria [NG]', 'Ekiti', 'Ado', 30798, 2660, 160, 1, '2024-11-16', NULL, 378, NULL, '1', 'TSLCTECHFEST2.0', NULL, '231rcfre2', 2585, '#tslctechfest2.0, #bytes&rights', 'paid', 'single', '1500', NULL, NULL, 'a:1:{s:40:\"SG93IHdvdWxkIHlvdSBsaWtlIHRvIGF0dGVuZD8=\";a:6:{s:2:\"id\";s:40:\"SG93IHdvdWxkIHlvdSBsaWtlIHRvIGF0dGVuZD8=\";s:8:\"question\";s:29:\"How would you like to attend?\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"multiple\";s:7:\"options\";a:2:{i:0;s:9:\"Physical \";i:1;s:7:\"Virtual\";}s:8:\"required\";b:0;s:7:\"specify\";b:0;}}', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'NGN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Event', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#000000', '', '<p>Thank you for registering for TSLC TECH FEST 2.0</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Get ready for an exciting lineup of workshops, keynote speakers, and valuable networking opportunities.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Stay tuned for updates, including the event schedule and speaker announcements.</p><p>We look forward to seeing you there</p>', NULL, NULL),
