(403, 'Ibadan Hangouts Owambe', 'EVT_1719765438294732141732182736514', '<p>Join us for the OWAMBE Extra, a cultural festival concept celebrating its 6th year anniversary by Ibadan Hangout. Experience the rich cultural heritage and diverse traditions of Owambe in the heart of Ibadan with thrilling performances, vibrant displays, and alluring entertainment. Dont miss out on this culturally exciting event!</p><p>The event includes a lineup of sensational music, dance, and cultural showcases. Secure your tickets early and be a part of this unforgettable celebration.</p>', '2024-12-27', '2024-12-27', '2024/11/21/uploads/1732182702642780image.jpg', '1671808628e9ala802t0r99cxniarle623ed', '10:52:16', '2024-11-21', '2024/11/21/uploads/1732182702642780image.jpg', 0, '11:00', 'Matrix, BCOS, Bashorun, Ibadan', 'IH', '<p>Join us for the OWAMBE Extra, a cultural festival concept celebrating its 6th year anniversary by Ibadan Hangout. Experience the rich cultural heritage and diverse traditions of Owambe in the heart of Ibadan with thrilling performances, vibrant displays, and alluring entertainment. Dont miss out on this culturally exciting event!</p><p>The event includes a lineup of sensational music, dance, and cultural showcases. Secure your tickets early and be a part of this unforgettable celebration.</p>', '', '', 'show', NULL, NULL, 'Nigeria [NG]', 'Oyo', 'Ibadan', 31064, 2677, 160, 1, '2024-12-31', NULL, 2000, NULL, '1', 'Ibadanhangoutowambe', NULL, '231r23cfre2', 115, 'Owambe, Ibadan, Cultural, Festival', 'paid', 'categorized', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'NGN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Event', NULL, NULL, '+2348139065694', 'a:2:{s:52:\"V2hhdCBpcyB0aGUgZHJlc3MgY29kZSBmb3IgdGhlIGV2ZW50Pw==\";a:3:{s:2:\"id\";s:52:\"V2hhdCBpcyB0aGUgZHJlc3MgY29kZSBmb3IgdGhlIGV2ZW50Pw==\";s:8:\"question\";s:37:\"What is the dress code for the event?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:118:\"Attendees are encouraged to dress in traditional or culturally inspired attire to celebrate t